snippet.title: Amber Heard Practices ‘Yard Yoga’ With The Girls | Splash News TV
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is practicing “yard yoga” for a little relaxation with the girls after wrapping up filming Justice League, and reportedly ramping up her relationship with Elon Musk. 

Subscribe now for the latest Daily Hollywood Celebrity Splash TV News: https://goo.gl/JaLP0U

Best Daily Splash News Daily Celebrity Playlist: https://goo.gl/QsxT0r

We guess Amber Heard just wants to show off how free and flexible she is now that she’s moved on from a very tumultuous divorce from Johnny Depp. 

The 31-year-old showed off her form by practicing “yard yoga” with some girlfriends, and it appears that Amber is in a much better position these days, and taking in all that wellness after returning back to Los Angeles from Australia. 

It clearly seems like Amber has a day off here, but her career is looking better as well. She’ll reportedly star as Mera in the highly anticipated Justice League series, who is the wife of Aquaman. 

Her real life romance isn’t with a superhero though… It’s with the Tesla billionaire, Elon Musk. So, we’re guessing things are pretty electric on that front as well. 

In fact, according to People magazine, “It’s definitely not a casual relationship. That’s not Elon. He doesn’t do anything casually.” 

So, even if the yard yoga is relaxing, sounds like they might be reaching “ludicrous mode” soon.
